import { Col, Container , Row, Card} from "react-bootstrap";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

const Collections = () => {
    return ( 
            <Container>
                <Row>
                <Col> 
                <Card>
                  <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>All Collection List</Card.Title>
                  <Link to="/collection">Collection 1(4)</Link>
                  <Link to="/collection">Collection 2(4)</Link>
                  <Link to="/collection">Collection 3(4)</Link>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>
                </Row>
                
                <Row>
                <Col> 
                <Card>
                  <Card.Body>
                  <Card.Title>Total Products in Collection</Card.Title>
                  <Link to="/collection">(4)</Link>
                  <Card.Text>Collection Name</Card.Text>
                  <Card.Text>Collection Description (with markdown formatting support)</Card.Text>
                  <Card.Text>Collection topic (one value from the predefined list, for example, “Books”, “Signs”, “Silverware”)</Card.Text>
                  <Card.Text>Collection image</Card.Text>
                </Card.Body>
                </Card>
                </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
     );
}
 
export default Collections;
